#

Portocalopita

$15
320 kcal
Difficulty: 60%

Allergens:

DairyEggs

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianNut-FreeDessert

Tags:

GourmetDessertCakes

Description

A delightful Greek orange phyllo cake soaked in a fragrant syrup, perfect for a sweet indulgence.

Ingredients

  • Phyllo dough: 1 package
  • Oranges: 4, zested and juiced
  • Sugar: 1 cup
  • Butter: 1/2 cup, melted
  • Eggs: 3
  • Baking powder: 1 tsp
  • Vanilla extract: 1 tsp
  • Water: 1 cup
